## REPL Patterns

### Start and access the system

```bash
export JWT_SECRET="dev-secret-minimum-32-characters"
clojure -M:repl-clj
```

```clojure
(go)    ; start system

;; Access a running component
(def user-svc (get integrant.repl.state/system :boundary/user-service))

;; Test a service function directly (bypass HTTP)
;; (user-svc/list-users user-svc {:limit 10})

;; After editing code
(reset)   ; reload changed namespaces and restart

;; After changing a defrecord definition
(halt)
(go)
```

### Query the database directly

```clojure
(require '[next.jdbc :as jdbc])
(def ds (get-in integrant.repl.state/system [:boundary/db-context :datasource]))
(jdbc/execute! ds ["SELECT * FROM users LIMIT 5"])
```

